name: New Benches/Old Memories
description:
This is another park in the old neighborhood. For over 100 years, neighbors and friends would gather here to kibbitz, feed the birds, and watch their children play. They installed new benches here recently, but the sound of joy and happiness still fill the air. I feel her spirit here.

3840x2160 JPEG

Photo by Jason Charnick
Taken in the Bronx, NY, USA
